<p>Welcome <%= @email %>!</p>

<p>You have to confirm your account by <%= (@user.created_at + User.allow_unconfirmed_access_for).strftime('%b %d, %Y') %>(in <%= (((@user.created_at + User.allow_unconfirmed_access_for).to_date) - Date.current).to_i %> days). After this, you won't be able to signin to Timblee.</p>

<p>You can confirm your account email through the link below:</p>

<p><%= link_to 'Confirm my account', confirmation_url(@resource, confirmation_token: @token) %></p>
